#define R(p,a,r)mix(a*dot(p,a),p,cos(r))+sin(r)*cross(p,a)
#define H(h)(cos((h)*6.3+vec3(0,23,21))*.5+.5)

void mainImage(out vec4 O, vec2 C)
{
    O=vec4(0);
    vec3 p,q,r=iResolution,
        d=normalize(vec3((C-.5*r.xy)/r.y,1.));
    for(
        float g,i,e,f,t=iTime;
        i++<99.;
        O.xyz+=mix(vec3(1),H(f),.6)*.01/exp(i*i*e)
        )
            p=d*g,
            p.z+=t*3.,
            p=R(p,vec3(.577),.5),
            q=floor(p/6.),
            q=sin(26.*(2.6*q+3.*q.yzx+1e-3)),
            f=dot(q,q.yxz),
            p=R(mod(p,6.)-3.,normalize(H(f)*2.-1.),t),
            g+=e=f>0.?.5:length(p-clamp(p,-.8,.8))*.6-.1;
}
